title: Happy Campers (2001)
description:
When a summer camp director gets injured, the diverse group of college freshmen counselors take charge and spice up the everyday routine of the camp.

I personally give the movie a 7.5/10; I think that some voters on IMDb frowned upon the sexual content expressed for this, not so normal teen camp movie.
